marytts.signalproc.sinusoidal

Class SinusoidalTrack

  • java.lang.Object
    • marytts.signalproc.sinusoidal.SinusoidalTrack

  • public class SinusoidalTrack
extends Object
    A sinusoidal track is a collection of matched (amplitude,frequency,phase) triplets which represents a "relatively" stationary time-frequency partition of a signal
    Author:
    Oytun Türk
